=== Fri Jun 19 06:05:56 PM EDT 2026 ===
STAGE 5 'rondo3v1' @u640. *** PASSING NOT EMERGING *** carry passed gate earlier. rondo3v1 STUCK? flagged at u400, u500, u600: pass_per_min=0.16/0.00/0.08 vs floor 2.0. poss oscillates 0.22-0.56, score flat ~0.50 (NEW BESTs are marginal 0.514->0.544). entropy stuck high ~6.2-6.5 (policy basically not committing). gd/ep noisy. realpass=1.00 only on the rare tick a release happens -- so the agent CAN complete a pass but almost never attempts one; it hoards/dribbles and push-spams (push/min 3.5-6.7).
VERDICT: STUCK / degenerate (ball-hoarding, no pass attempts). This is the failure mode the run guards against.
REC: trigger the GUIDED-BOOTSTRAPPING pass kickstart for rondo stages -- seed pass_attempts via a shaped reward / scripted demonstrations so a release-toward-teammate gets positive credit (current reward likely rewards retention only -> local optimum of dribbling). Also: the high stuck entropy suggests the pass action's advantage is ~0; consider an explicit pass-attempt bonus or temporarily lowering ent target. Without a pass kickstart, rondo3v1->4v2->buildup will all stall on pass/min floors.
